<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LAMP Stack - Powered by Ansible</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #0e0e0e;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color: #1c1c1c;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            animation: slideIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .banner {
            background-color: #ee0000;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

        .banner h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5em;
        }

        .banner p {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .info-box {
            background-color: #2d2d2d;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .info-box:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .info-box h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #ee0000;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .info-box p {
            color: #bbbbbb;
            font-size: 1em;
        }

        .powered-by {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #ffffff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .powered-by img {
            width: 200px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from {
                transform: translateY(50px);
                opacity: 0;
            }
            to {
                transform: translateY(0);
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="banner">
            <h1>LAMP Stack Installed!</h1>
            <p>Your server is running a fully operational LAMP stack.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>RHEL</h2>
                <p>The backbone of your server, <strong>Red Hat Enterprise Linux (RHEL)</strong> provides a stable and secure environment.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>Apache</h2>
                <p>The powerful web server that delivers your content to the world.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>MySQL</h2>
                <p>Reliable database management for your applicationâ€™s data needs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h2>PHP</h2>
                <p>Dynamic scripting language that makes your web applications interactive.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="powered-by">
            <p>Installed via</p>
            <img src="https://www.redhat.com/rhdc/managed-files/Logo-Red_Hat-Ansible_Automation_Platform-A-Standard-RGB_0.svg"
                alt="Ansible Automation Platform Logo">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
